    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 7th level, the light within you disorients those that try to fight against it. Once per turn, when you inflict the blinded condition, you can spend 3 chakra to force the blinded creature to make a Constitution saving throw against your ninjutsu save DC, being slowed until the end of their next turn on a failed save.</p>",
